    {
        "content": "<p>I just had a mentee think they have to do <code>x.py install</code> to do their development because that's what it says in the quick-start guide of <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/README.md\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/README.md\">https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/README.md</a></p>",
        "id": 154409391,
        "sender_full_name": "RalfJ",
        "timestamp": 1546609085
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>A much better place for them to find would have been <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#building\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#building\">https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#building</a></p>",
        "id": 154409424,
        "sender_full_name": "RalfJ",
        "timestamp": 1546609134
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I wonder if it is worth putting that more prominently in the README, or putting the manual install instructions (which we dont really want anyone to use) further down or even into a separate file.</p>",
        "id": 154409515,
        "sender_full_name": "RalfJ",
        "timestamp": 1546609234
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Cc <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"116011\">@Steve Klabnik</span></p>",
        "id": 154409518,
        "sender_full_name": "RalfJ",
        "timestamp": 1546609244
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"120791\">@RalfJ</span>  we might want to prominently link to the rustc guide in the readme if not done already?</p>",
        "id": 154436650,
        "sender_full_name": "centril",
        "timestamp": 1546635409
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>like \"this readme may be outdated... refer to the rustc guide first\"</p>",
